title: Sidewall, 1905–15
medium: Machine-printed on paper, textured ground, mica
description:
Small circular floral medallions with diaper floral swag, foliate swag, and connected by vining. Small individual leaves in between medallions and vining. Background has stripes of green and mica gold. Ground is green and embossed with foliate scroll pattern. Printed in greens, gold mica, pinks, and yellow. 
Printed in selvedge: "166"

tombstone.epitaph:
Sidewall, 1905–15.
1905–15. Machine-printed on paper, textured ground, mica. Gift of Victorian Collectibles. 1979-91-1212.
